<h2>6. Canva Design Instructions</h2>

<h3>Creating a Professional Email Signature in Canva</h3>

<div class="step-box">
<h3>Step 1: Create New Design</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Go to <strong>canva.com</strong> and log in</li>
  <li>Click <strong>"Create a design"</strong></li>
  <li>Click <strong>"Custom size"</strong></li>
  <li>Enter dimensions: <strong>600 x 200 pixels</strong></li>
  <li>Click <strong>"Create new design"</strong></li>
</ol>
</div>

<div class="step-box">
<h3>Step 2: Upload Brand Assets</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Click <strong>"Uploads"</strong> in left sidebar</li>
  <li>Click <strong>"Upload files"</strong></li>
  <li>Navigate to: <code>/home/user/premier-lead-marketing/email-signatures/logos/</code></li>
  <li>Upload <strong>plm-logo-stacked.svg</strong></li>
  <li>Also upload any icons needed from <code>/icons/</code> folder</li>
</ol>
</div>

<div class="step-box">
<h3>Step 3: Design Layout</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Drag your uploaded logo to the left side</li>
  <li>Add a vertical line (Elements → Lines) - color: #3b82f6, 3px width</li>
  <li>Add text elements on the right:</li>
</ol>

<p><strong>Text Elements to Add:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Name:</strong> Inter Bold, 18pt, color #1e293b</li>
  <li><strong>Title:</strong> Inter Medium, 13pt, color #3b82f6</li>
  <li><strong>Email:</strong> Inter Regular, 12pt, color #64748b</li>
  <li><strong>Website:</strong> Inter Regular, 12pt, color #60a5fa</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="step-box">
<h3>Step 4: Add CTA Button (Optional)</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Add a rectangle shape (Elements → Shapes)</li>
  <li>Set corner radius to 6px</li>
  <li>Set fill color to #3b82f6</li>
  <li>Add text: "Book Your Free Marketing Audit"</li>
  <li>Text: white (#ffffff), 12pt, bold</li>
</ol>
</div>

<div class="step-box">
<h3>Step 5: Export</h3>
<ol>
  <li>Click <strong>"Share"</strong> button (top right)</li>
  <li>Click <strong>"Download"</strong></li>
  <li>Select <strong>PNG</strong> format</li>
  <li>Click <strong>"Download"</strong></li>
</ol>
</div>

