<h2>8. Troubleshooting</h2>

<h3>Images Not Showing</h3>
<div class="warning">
<p><strong>Problem:</strong> Logo or images appear as broken links.</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Images must be hosted online. Upload the logo files to your website at <code>premierleadmarketing.ai/email-signatures/logos/</code> and update the image URLs in the HTML templates.</p>
</div>

<h3>Formatting Looks Wrong</h3>
<div class="warning">
<p><strong>Problem:</strong> Signature looks different than expected.</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Different email clients render HTML differently. For consistent results, export your signature as a single PNG image from Canva and insert that image instead.</p>
</div>

<h3>Signature Too Large</h3>
<div class="warning">
<p><strong>Problem:</strong> Signature takes up too much space in emails.</p>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong> Use the <code>signature-compact.html</code> template or reduce the logo size in Canva to 80-100px width.</p>
</div>

